Sunset Paws Website Intake Checklist

• Pet Information

  • Name, Breed, and Age

  • Mobility Status (e.g., independent, needs sling/harness, uses cart)

  • Specific Medical Conditions (e.g., Kidney disease, Arthritis, Cognitive Dysfunction)

  • Current Medication Schedule (Oral, Topical, etc.)

• Care Needs

  • The Respite Break (2-3 hour window)

  • The Stationary Day (Full 8-hour workday supervision)

  • The Legacy Stay (Overnight/24-hour care?

  • The Traveling Companion (Support for trips/vacations)

• Home/Office Setup (For Stationary Care)

  • Dedicated workspace available

  • Reliable Wi-Fi for remote work

• Goals for Care

  • "I need a mental health break/errand time."

  • "I am traveling and need a medical specialist onsite."

  • "I need help with intensive hospice/palliative monitoring."
